## `<file-level: constants>`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-schema-1 -->

### Purpose
DDL, PRAGMAs, and the current schema version. Consumed by `mkfs.py` (first-time setup) and `fs.py` (connection configuration on open).

### Postconditions
- `SCHEMA_VERSION == 1`.
- `DEFAULT_CHUNK_SIZE == 65536` (64 KiB).
- `ROOT_INODE == 1`.
- `MAXSYMLINKS == 40`.

### Implementation Notes

```python
SCHEMA_VERSION = 1
DEFAULT_CHUNK_SIZE = 65536
ROOT_INODE = 1
MAXSYMLINKS = 40
```

